            "name": "Anna Salario",
            "startSeconds": 325,
            "endSeconds": 527,
            "summary": "Speaking on behalf of classified members, she asked the board for compensation comparable to the stipends teachers are receiving, arguing classified employees' responsibilities have increased significantly during the pandemic."
          },
          {
            "name": "Sue Jorgensen",
            "startSeconds": 614,
            "endSeconds": 760,
            "summary": "Echoed the classified compensation concern from an equity standpoint, noting that classified staff and teachers working side-by-side are receiving very different financial recognition for the same in-person risks."
          }
        ],
        "consent": false,
